<sup>3</sup>, <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Krumholz%20HM"[Author]' class="usa-link" aria-describedby="id8"><span class="name western">Harlan M Krumholz</span></a><div hidden="hidden" id="id8">
<h3>
<span class="name western">Harlan M Krumholz</span>, <span class="degrees">MD, SM</span>
</h3>
<div class="p">
<sup>5</sup>Section of Cardiovascular Medicine and the Robert Wood Johnson Clinical Scholars Program, Department of Medicine, Yale University School of Medicine, and Section of Health Policy and Administration, Yale School of Public Health; and the Center for Outcomes Research and Evaluation, Yale-New Haven Hospital, New Haven, Connecticut</div>
<div class="p">Find articles by <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Krumholz%20HM"[Author]' class="usa-link"><span class="name western">Harlan M Krumholz</span></a>
</div>
